{lang-eng}Krīstēsunandu manaku pāpa kṣamāpaṇa kaligenu 1 andhakara sambandhamaina
Adhikāramulanuṇḍi viḍudaladorike 2 prabhunakanni viṣayamulalō
Taginaṭṭugā naḍucukonumu 2 nīvu prēmanu kaligi yuṇḍumu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Prabhu yesu adr̥ṣyuṇḍaina dēvuni rūpamu galavāḍu. Sarvasr̥uṣṭiki kartayu tane
Ninnu nutana sr̥uṣṭiga jese prabhunakanni viṣayamulalō
Nīvu ellappuḍu anandinnchumu taginaṭṭugā naḍachukonumu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Mrrutulalo nuṇḍi modaṭa leche yunnavaḍu yesuprabhu manalanu taṇḍri
Rajyamunaku varasulugā jesiyunnaḍu. Prabhunakanni viṣayamulalo
Taginaṭṭuga naḍacukonumu nīvu yelanimmu samadhanamu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Krīstesunandu sarvasampūrṇata niṇḍi yunnadi siluva maraṇamu
Dvarane manala taṇḍrito samadhāna parache prabhunakanni viṣayamulalō
Taginaṭṭugā naḍucukonumu nīvu dīrgasaantamu kaligi yuṇḍumu.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Samasta sr̥ṣṭhiki prakaṭimpa baḍina suvārtanu viḍuvaka viśvāsamanda
Nilicina yeḍala śrīnīvāmahimanu pondedavu prabhunakanni viṣayamulalō
Taginaṭṭugā naḍacukonumu nīvu dayāḷutvamu kanuparacumu{/lang-eng}
